2026-04-07 20:55:31.924 | INFO     | app.agent.toolcall:think:89 - 🔧 Tool arguments: {"code": "import requests\nimport json\nimport time\n\n# 使用Semantic Scholar API搜索论文\ndef search_semantic_scholar(query, limit=10):\n    \"\"\"使用Semantic Scholar API搜索论文\"\"\"\n    base_url = \"https://api.semanticscholar.org/graph/v1/paper/search\"\n    params = {\n        'query': query,\n        'limit': limit,\n        'fields': 'title,authors,year,abstract,url,venue,citationCount'\n    }\n    \n    try:\n        response = requests.get(base_url, params=params, timeout=30)\n        response.raise_for_status()\n        data = response.json()\n        \n        papers = []\n        for paper in data.get('data', []):\n            papers.append({\n                'title': paper.get('title', 'No title'),\n                'authors': ', '.join([author['name'] for author in paper.get('authors', [])]),\n                'year': paper.get('year', 'Unknown'),\n                'abstract': paper.get('abstract', 'No abstract'),\n                'url': paper.get('url', 'No URL'),\n                'venue': paper.get('venue', 'Unknown venue'),\n                'citationCount': paper.get('citationCount', 0)\n            })\n        \n        return papers\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error fetching from Semantic Scholar: {e}\")\n        return []\n\n# 搜索粒子群算法改进相关论文\nprint(\"正在搜索粒子群算法改进相关论文...\")\n\n# 定义搜索关键词\nsearch_queries = [\n    \"particle swarm optimization improvements\",\n    \"PSO algorithm enhancements\",\n    \"adaptive particle swarm optimization\",\n    \"hybrid particle swarm optimization\",\n    \"multi-objective particle swarm optimization\"\n]\n\nall_papers = []\nfor query in search_queries:\n    print(f\"\\n搜索: {query}\")\n    papers = search_semantic_scholar(query, limit=5)\n    all_papers.extend(papers)\n    print(f\"找到 {len(papers)} 篇论文\")\n    time.sleep(1)  # 避免请求过快\n\n# 去重\nunique_papers = []\nseen_titles = set()\nfor paper in all_papers:\n    if paper['title'] not in seen_titles:\n        seen_titles.add(paper['title'])\n        unique_papers.append(paper)\n\nprint(f\"\\n总共找到 {len(unique_papers)} 篇不重复的论文\")\n\n# 按年份和引用数排序\nunique_papers.sort(key=lambda x: (x['year'], x['citationCount']), reverse=True)\n\n# 显示结果\nprint(\"\\n=== 粒子群算法改进相关论文 ===\")\nfor i, paper in enumerate(unique_papers[:15], 1):\n    print(f\"\\n{i}. {paper['title']}\")\n    print(f\"   作者: {paper['authors']}\")\n    print(f\"   年份: {paper['year']}, 引用: {paper['citationCount']}\")\n    print(f\"   期刊/会议: {paper['venue']}\")\n    print(f\"   摘要: {paper['abstract'][:150]}...\" if paper['abstract'] else \"   摘要: 无摘要\")\n    print(f\"   链接: {paper['url']}\")\n\n# 分析改进方向\nprint(\"\\n=== 粒子群算法的主要改进方向分析 ===\")\nimprovement_directions = {\n    \"自适应PSO\": 0,\n    \"混合算法\": 0,\n    \"多目标PSO\": 0,\n    \"并行PSO\": 0,\n    \"约束处理\": 0,\n    \"动态环境\": 0\n}\n\n# 根据标题和摘要分析改进方向\nfor paper in unique_papers:\n    title_lower = paper['title'].lower()\n    abstract_lower = paper['abstract'].lower() if paper['abstract'] else \"\"\n    \n    if 'adaptive' in title_lower or 'adaptive' in abstract_lower:\n        improvement_directions[\"自适应PSO\"] += 1\n    if 'hybrid' in title_lower or 'hybrid' in abstract_lower:\n        improvement_directions[\"混合算法\"] += 1\n    if 'multi-objective' in title_lower or 'multiobjective' in title_lower:\n        improvement_directions[\"多目标PSO\"] += 1\n    if 'parallel' in title_lower or 'parallel' in abstract_lower:\n        improvement_directions[\"并行PSO\"] += 1\n    if 'constraint' in title_lower or 'constraint' in abstract_lower:\n        improvement_directions[\"约束处理\"] += 1\n    if 'dynamic' in title_lower or 'dynamic' in abstract_lower:\n        improvement_directions[\"动态环境\"] += 1\n\nprint(\"\\n改进方向统计:\")\nfor direction, count in improvement_directions.items():\n    print(f\"  {direction}: {count} 篇论文\")"}
